**Risks:**
- Exec env-var contract is provisional — the real claude/Agent-SDK adapter may
  need richer signalling (multiple outputs, structured result). Mitigation:
  single output file + env vars is the minimal reproduced contract; documented
  as the v1 contract; RunResult.Producer override (discovered skill version/model)
  is a future hook, echo req.Producer for now.
- Cross-platform: sh-script tests are POSIX. Mitigation: guard with runtime.GOOS
  and write the script via os.WriteFile + chmod (no shell invocation in prod code).
- Otherwise low — mirrors two established, tested exec call sites.

