1. SCRATCH HYGIENE (correctness bug): before exec, remove any stale <ScratchDir>/output and RemoveAll+MkdirAll <ScratchDir>/inputs (fresh). Otherwise a command that exits 0 without writing output would return a PRIOR run's stale output. Tests: stale-output present + command writes nothing -> ErrOutputMissing (not stale bytes); stale-input file not in this req -> not leaked into the run.
